 ♪"},{"s":37.1,"e":40.66,"text":"♪ Bless the homeless, hopeless, roaming ♪"},{"s":40.66,"e":44.3,"text":"♪ Guide them safely, softly, homeward ♪"},{"s":44.3,"e":47.72,"text":"♪ Warm the frozen, broken, chosen ♪"},{"s":47.72,"e":50.9,"text":"♪ Lift the fallen, called forgiven ♪"},{"s":50.9,"e":54.28,"text":"♪ For the hungry, empty, aching ♪"},{"s":54.28,"e":57.94,"text":"♪ Bring them bread and grace unshaken ♪"},{"s":57.94,"e":61.7,"text":"♪ For the poor with doors unopened ♪"},{"s":61.7,"e":64.96,"text":"♪ Bring them hope and hearts awoken ♪"},{"s":64.96,"e":68.52,"text":"♪ For disabled souls still striving ♪"},{"s":68.52,"e":72.04,"text":"♪ Give them strength and sacred rising ♪"},{"s":72.04,"e":75.36,"text":"♪ Guard their bodies, minds, and spirits ♪"},{"s":75.36,"e":78.8,"text":"♪ Let them know your love is nearest ♪"},{"s":78.8,"e":82.34,"text":"♪ Break addiction, shame, affliction, whoo! ♪"},{"s":82.34,"e":87.86,"text":"♪ Turn our pity into mission, whoo! ♪"},{"s":87.86,"e":91.18,"text":"♪ Serving, whoo! More forgiving, whoo! ♪"},{"s":91.18,"e":93.2,"text":"♪ Less deserving, whoo! ♪"},{"s":93.2,"e":96.32,"text":"♪ Restore the crushed and crying, whoo! ♪"},{"s":96.32,"e":99.66,"text":"♪ Raise the weak who feel like dying, whoo! ♪"},{"s":99.66,"e":102.7,"text":"♪ Light the street and night and shelter ♪"},{"s":102.7,"e":106.78,"text":"♪ Be their helper, healer, welcomer, whoo! ♪"},{"s":106.78,"e":110.18,"text":"♪ Grant us courage clear and burning, whoo! ♪"},{"s":110.18,"e":113.6,"text":"♪ Wisdom deep and hearts still learning, whoo! ♪"},{"s":113.6,"e":116.7,"text":"♪ Have measure, whoo! But full treasure, whoo! ♪"},{"s":116.7,"e":121.9,"text":"♪ Love beyond all earthly measure, amen! Amen! ♪"},{"s":121.9,"e":127.74,"text":"♪ Let grace awaken, no one lost! And unforsaken! Twice! ♪"},{"s":127.74,"e":135.46,"text":"♪ Beside the least and small, Mercy, mercy, cover all! ♪"},{"s":135.46,"e":142.7,"text":"♪ Oooh, oooh, oooh! ♪"},{"s":142.7,"e":146.14,"text":"♪ Oh! ♪"}],"duration":157.32000732421875,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:33:01.249Z","model":"whisper-1"}